hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1805c81b693ba6409f946f2080a354f9f795b17c","tid":1363313,"uid":247122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99e3271a2e3ebfad50cf22bf3abf3798a4239f28","tid":1363313,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:51:07.000Z","msg":"不接受特赦警隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11d60c8a2048d785c381d5359b7ef28301bab7e","tid":1363313,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:52:42.000Z","msg":"好似有個post講過應該要啲咩人員組成市民先會接受"},{"pid":"b91af8825811e6cd97988d4301fc7d4911a5467b","tid":1363313,"uid":247122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:52:51.000Z","msg":"幫手推plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a838d83c4af6ec92d6bf373eeab5b97f3d0338cf","tid":1363313,"uid":182192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbf2560bb77437227410d650d3dbe82184a96d5b","tid":1363313,"uid":247122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"近排開始有政治取態一向係中立甚至係親建制和商界嘅人物放風話唔反對成立獨立調查委員會，獨立調查漸漸變成社會共識。雖然有傳林鄭暫時唔會考慮，但係我認為政府礙於社會各方壓力，宣布成立獨立調查委員會只係時間問題。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過，就算政府真係成立獨立調查委員會，大家都千祈唔能夠就此收貨！因為政府版本嘅「獨立調查」，有機會同大家所諗嘅有所落差，甚至成為一種為政權服務的邪惡工具！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先，政府版本嘅獨立調查有機會放生警隊！</span></span>眾所周知，警隊中人極力反對成立調查委員會。林鄭作為朝廷鷹犬，在宣佈成立獨立調查委員會嘅同時，也定必顧及警隊士氣。近日有篇由知名政治公關寫嘅文或者預視到獨委會嘅做法：<br />\n//恢復警民互信，是維持警隊士氣的最重要基礎，而肯定獨立調查會有幫助。如果政府有決心進行獨立調查，又真的重視警隊士氣，就應該積極與警隊商議，訂立盡量不影響警員士氣的調查安排，例如凡是願意向調查提供真相和真誠意見的警員，就不予追究。//<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/文摘/article/20190724/s00022/1563887150542/協商獨立調查-突破危城困局（文-盧子健）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%96%87%E6%91%98%2Farticle%2F20190724%2Fs00022%2F1563887150542%2F%E5%8D%94%E5%95%86%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4%E5%8D%B1%E5%9F%8E%E5%9B%B0%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87-%E7%9B%A7%E5%AD%90%E5%81%A5%EF%BC%89&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=5dc3c3bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%96%87%E6%91%98%2Farticle%2F20190724%2Fs00022%2F1563887150542%2F%E5%8D%94%E5%95%86%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4%E5%8D%B1%E5%9F%8E%E5%9B%B0%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87-%E7%9B%A7%E5%AD%90%E5%81%A5%EF%BC%89&h=e8b1ec9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/文摘/article/20190724/s00022/1563887150542/協商獨立調查-突破危城困局（文-盧子健）</a><br />\n<br />\n換而之，獨委會有機會效法1977年警廉衝突嘅做法，特赦違法嘅警員嘅罪責（只要佢哋提供「真相和真誠意見」）！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其次，政府版本嘅獨立調查有機會成為打壓示威者嘅工具！</span></span>政界中人所提倡嘅獨立調查普遍提倡不止調查警隊，亦包括調查示威者嘅一方。個人其實唔反對從呢種方向嚟做從而還原事件真相，不過大前提係律政司須承諾撤銷對示威者嘅一切控罪。否則，獨委會唔單止唔能夠幫助尋找公義，更會令更多示威者負上刑事責任！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後一點，政府版本嘅獨立調查有機會放生政府！</span></span>從六一二警方使用過度武力到上星期白衣人元朗發動恐怖襲擊，究竟只係警方責任，抑或涉及更高層（行政長官、政府高官甚至行政會議）嘅決定？如果獨立調查委員會不能賦予足夠權力同權限去調查任何一方嘅話，就會變得綁手綁腳，既不能揭開事件真相，反為這不仁政權製造「合法性」！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我重申，就算政府真係成立獨立調查委員會，大家都千祈唔能夠就此收貨！必須繼續運用民間監察力量，金睛火眼去檢視獨委會嘅組成、權力範圍同埋調查進展！另外亦必須繼續堅持其餘四大訴求！<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳！！！非常重要！！！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ce1f0feb8f1020a02ca05238ced8cfd641221c","tid":1363313,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:53:31.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n因為而家要既係真普選<br />\n<br />\n冇既下一步就係要獨立"},{"pid":"723d437da24cb3071a0b71c18c50503477503d67","tid":1363313,"uid":29756,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:54:02.000Z","msg":"5個訴求講到尾咪又係幫個制度貼膠布<br />\n有邊個講真政府肯做會收貨<br />\n仲係到留戀5大訴求做乜<br />\n幫夠個政府未"},{"pid":"179e1ff688a940a0fea348e611514be6bbe49f7e","tid":1363313,"uid":247122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba13b1c0c8a96864a7199df0165c78b292304c2","tid":1363313,"uid":247122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3962d922e8ad5e0ddea74aa0976e23cbbfa0a520","tid":1363313,"uid":247122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:56:19.000Z","msg":"幫手推及share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9631bcb2358d9a4e3033eb2eba1255309f7244ad","tid":1363313,"uid":247122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a218737b1f53340998ceb19da77ed1f5d4d7be5","tid":1363313,"uid":247122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6fc0537b6d6c44288ae18c466134f5fca6108a","tid":1363313,"uid":247122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7840b3e5a0e61101d93f70fac9f8e5447c6a71c8","tid":1363313,"uid":247122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ed401f6426b578f0674bba595ea4b6e502a595","tid":1363313,"uid":286990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:59:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkpopo.weebly.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/